enrichedData.name: Ryobi 18V ONE+ Drill Driver Starter Kit
enrichedData.description: The RYOBI 18V ONE+ Drill Driver Starter Kit allows you to undertake a wide variety of DIY projects, household repairs and maintenance jobs. It’s a great value option for anyone looking to start their home toolkit. It features an 18V ONE+ Drill Driver, one of the most essential tools you can own - as well as an 18V ONE+ 1.5Ah Battery, 1.5A Charger and a Double-Sided Screwdriver Bit.  Use the Drill Driver to drill holes and drive screws into timber, steel and plastic. Choose between 24 clutch settings to get the right amount of torque (twisting power) for driving screws and other fasteners. Its 13mm chuck makes it quick and easy to change over accessories.Switch between the Drill Driver’s two speed modes for different tasks. Speed 1 (slow) is suitable for driving screws; speed 2 )fast) is best for drilling. The in-built LED light illuminates your work in dark and confined areas. Hold extra screws and fasteners for easy access with the magnetic screw tray.Power the Drill Driver and other small tools from the ONE+ range with the 1.5Ah Battery. Use it to power hammer drills, sanders, lights, secateurs, power scrubbers, radios and a lot more! RYOBI’s Intelli-Cell™ technology monitors and balances individual cells for longer life and additional safety. The Battery’s on-board fuel gauge shows how much charge is left. The 1.5A Charger can charge any battery from the ONE+ range. Its compact design takes up little space in any workshop or garage.
